---
title: About Me
---

Being passionate about data in science and the science of data, I assume the role of a data-detective when hired: I conduct a thorough investigation to uncover the truth hidden within, while also doing the regular "police" work (cleaning, wrangling, etc.) on the data. I can guarantee exceptional performance without compromising rigor in the following fields:

-   Statistical modeling and inference - biostatitics, stochastic processes.

-   R - data analysis, package development, shiny apps.

-   Simulation - design and scaling of numerical experiments.

